      '**Pricing Breakdown:** ActiveCampaign offers several tiers designed to grow with your business. The Lite plan starts around **$29/month** (billed annually for 1,000 contacts), offering core email marketing and automation. The Plus plan, starting at **$49/month**, adds a built-in CRM, lead scoring, and advanced integrations. For professional businesses and agencies, the Professional plan begins at **$149/month** with predictive sending and attribution. Enterprise plans are custom-quoted. They also provide a generous **14-day free trial** to explore all features. Considering its capabilities, ActiveCampaign is absolutely worth the price if you leverage its full potential for lead nurturing software and advanced segmentation.',
